        <updateDate>2018-07-24T21:43:55Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Department of Veterans Affairs Creation of On-Site Treatment Systems Affording Veterans Improvements and Numerous General Safety Enhancements Act or the VA COST SAVINGS Enhancements Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) to install and operate an on-site regulated medical waste treatment system at each VA facility that would benefit from such a system's cost savings.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
